  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t老穆黨指揮槍，槍桿子裏出政權，政教合一，宗教指揮軍隊<br/>\n<br/>\r\n老毛也類似<br/>\n<br/>\r\n老穆思想統一全球，綠旗或黑旗插遍世界，穆罕默德思想千古留芳，永垂不朽，老毛嘛…………<br/>\n<br/>\r\n老穆像成功版的摩西，摩西及埃及利未人是政教合一，宗教改革的先驅，舊約說被神詛咒禁止進入應許之地，佛洛伊德說他在沙漠中不幸地被奴隸起義打死了<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly91cGxvYWQud2lraW1lZGlhLm9yZy93aWtpcGVkaWEvY29tbW9ucy85Lzk5L1RoZV9Qcm9waGV0X011aGFtbWFkX2FuZF90aGVfTXVzbGltX0FybXlfYXRfdGhlX0JhdHRsZV9vZl9VaHVkLF9mcm9tX3RoZV9TaXllci1pX05lYmksXzE1OTUuanBn\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/99/The_Prophet_Muhammad_and_the_Muslim_Army_at_the_Battle_of_Uhud,_from_the_Siyer-i_Nebi,_1595.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/99/The_Prophet_Muhammad_and_the_Muslim_Army_at_the_Battle_of_Uhud,_from_the_Siyer-i_Nebi,_1595.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/99/The_Prophet_Muhammad_and_the_Muslim_Army_at_the_Battle_of_Uhud,_from_the_Siyer-i_Nebi,_1595.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
